@host = http://127.0.0.1:5080
@token = demo-token

### 健康检查（无需 Token）
GET {{host}}/v1/health

### 领域列表
GET {{host}}/v1/domains
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 专利领域详情
GET {{host}}/v1/domains/patent
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 流式对话
POST {{host}}/v1/chat/stream
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "demo-session-001",
  "domain": "patent",
  "message": "今年新申请案件授权率是多少？",
  "stream": true,
  "messages": []
}

### DB-GPT 连通性（非 Mock 时有效）
GET {{host}}/v1/dbgpt/ping
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### DB-GPT 应用列表
GET {{host}}/v1/dbgpt/apps
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
